Text: now that i have downloaded this, may i humbly ask how do I install this in my ipad?? i would really appreciate a step by step instructions, thanks a lot.

1. jailbreak ur ipad (use google, it's really easy to find)
2. install appsync from cydia (google)
3. put your apps in the itunes library and sync it with ipad (google, hmm, did i mention it before?)
